<BR>-IceClad (good place, not very interesting though)<BR>-The Great Oowomp (more challenging I am thinking, plus loot)<BR>-WC Druid Rings/EC Rangers (seems challenging, with the whole, split, fear, kill ASAP deal)<BR>-Single Spectre in Feerott (seems challenging also, high risk of sudden death from trains, etc.)<BR>-Something I just thought of...I haven't been by this way recently, but I heard that all of the old CT mobs were moved outside into that little island entrance area - could I pull MoBs from in here and solo them?</P><P>Any suggestions/comments/questions are appreciated.</P><P>Also, I currently do not have my new pet, CoB, Resist Disease, the level 29 SoL Undead DoT, or Invoke Fear (anyone know where to get this?) but I will get them ASAP.</P><P><font size=1><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=54401" target="_blank">Azumaan</a></b><br>34 Erudite Necromancer<br>&lt;Dragon Maw&gt;<br>Mithaniel Marr</font id=size1></font></td>
